        "description": "JWT Authorization header using the Bearer scheme. </br>\r\n                      Enter 'Bearer' [space] and then your token in the text input below.\r\n                      </br>Example: 'Bearer 12345abcdef'",
        "name": "Authorization",
        "in": "header"
